Whitepaper — SocialFi42 (SCF)
1. Introduction

SocialFi42 is a decentralized social media platform built on Web3 principles, designed to give users full ownership of their data, content, and digital interactions.

Unlike traditional Web2 social networks where user data is controlled and monetized by centralized companies, SocialFi42 shifts ownership back to the users through blockchain technology.

The native token of the ecosystem is SCF (SocialFi Token), an ERC-20 token deployed on Ethereum-compatible networks.

2. Vision

The goal of SocialFi42 is to build a fully decentralized social ecosystem where:

Users own their data and identity
Content is transparently managed on-chain or token-linked
Value created by users is redistributed back to them
Creators are directly rewarded without intermediaries
